Development
-----------

For development setup, see `py-multiaddr contributing`_.

.. code-block:: bash

    # Clone the repository
    git clone https://github.com/multiformats/py-multiaddr.git
    cd py-multiaddr

    # Install in development mode
    pip install -e ".[dev]"

    # Run the development workflow
    make pr

